pesquisaveis.valor: (Select LISTAGG(ci.INSCRICAOCADASTRAL, ',') WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY CI.INSCRICAOCADASTRAL) from ITEMPROCESSODEBITO item inner join parcelavalordivida pvd on pvd.id = item.PARCELA_ID inner join valordivida vd on vd.id = pvd.VALORDIVIDA_ID inner join calculo on calculo.id = vd.CALCULO_ID inner join cadastro cad on cad.id = calculo.CADASTRO_ID left join cadastroeconomico cmc on cmc.id = cad.id left join cadastroimobiliario ci on ci.id = cad.id left join cadastrorural cr on cr.id = cad.id where item.PROCESSODEBITO_ID = pd.id AND ROWNUM <=10) like '%'||${VALOR_DIGITADO}||'%'

(Select listagg(cmc.INSCRICAOCADASTRAL, ',') within group (order by cmc.INSCRICAOCADASTRAL)     from ITEMPROCESSODEBITO item         inner join parcelavalordivida pvd on pvd.id = item.PARCELA_ID         inner join valordivida vd on vd.id = pvd.VALORDIVIDA_ID         inner join calculo on calculo.id = vd.CALCULO_ID         inner join cadastro cad on cad.id = calculo.CADASTRO_ID         left join cadastroeconomico cmc on cmc.id = cad.id         left join cadastroimobiliario ci on ci.id = cad.id         left join cadastrorural cr on cr.id = cad.id     where item.PROCESSODEBITO_ID = pd.id and ROWNUM <=10) like '%'||${VALOR_DIGITADO}||'%'

(Select coalesce(pf.NOME, pj.RAZAOSOCIAL) from ITEMPROCESSODEBITO item inner join parcelavalordivida pvd on pvd.id = item.PARCELA_ID inner join valordivida vd on vd.id = pvd.VALORDIVIDA_ID inner join calculo on calculo.id = vd.CALCULO_ID left join calculopessoa cp on vd.calculo_id = cp.calculo_id left join pessoafisica pf on cp.pessoa_id = pf.id left join pessoajuridica pj on cp.pessoa_id = pj.id left join cadastro cad on cad.id = calculo.CADASTRO_ID left join cadastroeconomico cmc on cmc.id = cad.id left join cadastroimobiliario ci on ci.id = cad.id left join cadastrorural cr on cr.id = cad.id where item.PROCESSODEBITO_ID = pd.id fetch first 1 rows only)

(Select coalesce(FORMATACPFCNPJ(pf.cpf), FORMATACPFCNPJ(pj.cnpj)) from ITEMPROCESSODEBITO item inner join parcelavalordivida pvd on pvd.id = item.PARCELA_ID inner join valordivida vd on vd.id = pvd.VALORDIVIDA_ID inner join calculo on calculo.id = vd.CALCULO_ID left join calculopessoa cp on vd.calculo_id = cp.calculo_id left join pessoafisica pf on cp.pessoa_id = pf.id left join pessoajuridica pj on cp.pessoa_id = pj.id left join cadastro cad on cad.id = calculo.CADASTRO_ID left join cadastroeconomico cmc on cmc.id = cad.id left join cadastroimobiliario ci on ci.id = cad.id left join cadastrorural cr on cr.id = cad.id where item.PROCESSODEBITO_ID = pd.id fetch first 1 rows only)

from:
from processodebito pd
inner join exercicio ex on pd.exercicio_id = ex.id
where pd.tipo = 'BAIXA'

tabelaveis.valorOrdenacao: (Select listagg(coalesce(to_char(cr.CODIGO), ci.inscricaocadastral, cmc.inscricaocadastral, coalesce(FORMATACPFCNPJ(pf.cpf), FORMATACPFCNPJ(pj.cnpj))), ', ') within group (order by pd.ID) from ITEMPROCESSODEBITO item inner join parcelavalordivida pvd on pvd.id = item.PARCELA_ID inner join valordivida vd on vd.id = pvd.VALORDIVIDA_ID inner join calculo on calculo.id = vd.CALCULO_ID left join calculopessoa cp on calculo.id = cp.calculo_id left join pessoa pe on cp.pessoa_id = pe.id left join pessoafisica pf on pe.id = pf.id left join pessoajuridica pj on pe.id = pj.id left join cadastro cad on cad.id = calculo.CADASTRO_ID left join cadastroeconomico cmc on cmc.id = cad.id left join cadastroimobiliario ci on ci.id = cad.id left join cadastrorural cr on cr.id = cad.id where item.PROCESSODEBITO_ID = pd.id and ROWNUM <=10)
tabelaveis.valor: (Select listagg(coalesce(to_char(cr.CODIGO), ci.inscricaocadastral, cmc.inscricaocadastral, coalesce(FORMATACPFCNPJ(pf.cpf), FORMATACPFCNPJ(pj.cnpj))), ', ') within group (order by pd.ID) from ITEMPROCESSODEBITO item inner join parcelavalordivida pvd on pvd.id = item.PARCELA_ID inner join valordivida vd on vd.id = pvd.VALORDIVIDA_ID inner join calculo on calculo.id = vd.CALCULO_ID left join calculopessoa cp on calculo.id = cp.calculo_id left join pessoa pe on cp.pessoa_id = pe.id left join pessoafisica pf on pe.id = pf.id left join pessoajuridica pj on pe.id = pj.id left join cadastro cad on cad.id = calculo.CADASTRO_ID left join cadastroeconomico cmc on cmc.id = cad.id left join cadastroimobiliario ci on ci.id = cad.id left join cadastrorural cr on cr.id = cad.id where item.PROCESSODEBITO_ID = pd.id and ROWNUM <=10)
